  "text": "The analogue of Corollary 6 for the non-reversible case will be obtained by combining Theorems 17, 18 and 19 below. Theorem 17 is from Dyer, Frieze and Jerrum [CITATION_1] , and Theorem 18 is a continuous-time version of the same result.",
